msgctxt "sn23.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyamāravagga "
msgstr "2. About Māra (2nd) "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 20. Vayadhammasutta → vaya (pts1)
msgctxt "sn23.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Vayadhammasutta "
msgstr "20. Liable To Vanish "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn23.20:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.20:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.20:1.3"
msgid "“‘vayadhammo, vayadhammo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of things being ‘liable to vanish’. "

msgctxt "sn23.20:1.4"
msgid "Katamo nu kho, bhante, vayadhammo”ti? "
msgstr "What is liable to vanish?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.20:1.5"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, vayadhammo, vedanā vayadhammo, saññā vayadhammo, saṅkhārā vayadhammo, viññāṇaṃ vayadhammo. "
msgstr "“Rādha, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are liable to vanish. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.20:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn23.20:1.7"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.20:1.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
